data.description: 2 bed/2 bath Villa in highly sought after Villages of Longwood in Ft. Pierce. Tile floors throughout the common areas with vinyl flooring and carpet in the bedrooms. The spacious kitchen opens up to the dining/living area. Large screened in porch for entertaining. The Community amenities include a clubhouse, library and two pools (one heated). Centrally located to downtown, I-95 and US1. Close to the hospital and schools.
